{"id":273781,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/环球主编胡锡进-不堪压力-微博申辩？/","date":"2013-01-09T18:04:11Z","modified":"2013-01-09T18:04:11Z","title":"环球主编胡锡进 不堪压力 微博申辩？","content":"<p>南周新年献辞事件后，《环球时报》接连发表社评为官方造势，声称“<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%E3%80%90%E5%BC%82%E9%97%BB%E8%A7%82%E6%AD%A2%E3%80%91%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5-%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E5%86%B7%E9%9D%99%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E3%80%8A%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E5%91%A8/\">中国媒体不可能成为同西方一样的媒体</a>”，并暗示南周事件<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%E3%80%90%E5%BC%82%E9%97%BB%E8%A7%82%E6%AD%A2%E3%80%91%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%8D%97%E6%96%B9%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E8%87%B4%E8%AF%BB%E8%80%85%E5%AE%9E%E5%9C%A8/\">与远在美国的陈光诚有关联</a>。1月7日晚，<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%AC%E6%8A%A5%E6%82%B2%E6%84%A4%E5%B1%88%E8%BE%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%9C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%A3%E9%83%A8%E4%BA%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%8E%8B%E9%98%B5%E5%8D%B0%E5%88%B7%E6%88%BF-%E4%BC%A0%E7%A4%BE%E9%95%BF/\">《新京报》主编戴自更拒绝转载《环球》的社评</a>；在中宣部副部长亲临压阵印刷房后仍不屈服，并口头提出辞职。<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%E3%80%90%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%AF%8D%E5%BA%93%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%AC%E6%8A%A5%E6%8B%92%E8%BD%BD%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E7%A6%81%E8%AF%8D-2013-1-8/\">新京报拒载一事</a>在网络传开后，使得本就已经对《环球时报》非常不满的网民们更添怒气，纷纷将矛头指向了《环球》及其主编胡锡进。胡锡进在新浪微博的认证账号也遭到许多网民的留言唾骂，包括著名演员<a href=\"href=&quot;http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%E4%BC%8A%E8%83%BD%E9%9D%99-%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5%E8%BF%99%E5%8F%AA%E7%8B%97/\">伊能静也加入到了谴责胡锡进的行列</a>。</p>\n<blockquote><p>背景新闻：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB-%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%A5%E3%80%8A%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5%E3%80%8B%E7%A4%BE%E8%AE%BA%E5%8F%AF%E8%80%BB/\">媒体人斥《环球时报》社论可耻</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E9%9F%B3-%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%A3%E9%83%A8%E5%BC%BA%E5%A5%B8%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB%E6%9D%83%E7%84%A6%E7%82%B9%E7%A7%BB%E8%87%B3%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%96%B0/\">中宣部强奸媒体自主权焦点移至北京新京报 </a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p>中国北京时间1月9日晚，有网民发现胡锡进在新浪发出如下微博后又迅速删除：</p>\n<blockquote><p>@胡锡进：弱弱地申辩一句：我们从没写过南周事件是“境外势力”操纵的，我现在也不这么认为。那是网络小编为增加转发故意引伸的。不好意思，小编也不容易。</p></blockquote>\n<div id=\"attachment_273782\" style=\"width: 581px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/胡锡进.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-273782\" title=\"胡锡进\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/胡锡进.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"571\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/胡锡进.jpg 571w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/胡锡进-300x226.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 571px) 100vw, 571px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">图片来源：Twitter @上宫乱</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>显然，网民们对胡锡进的自我申辩并不认同。下附新浪微博“胡锡进”的搜索结果截图：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/huxijin.png\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-273783\" title=\"huxijin\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/huxijin.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"518\" height=\"4398\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[8339,9240,21901,21876,15525]}